\define check-password(attempt) <% if [<__attempt__>match{$:/temp/password}] %>You're in!<% else %>Wrong password!<% endif %>

!! Authorization Bypass Demo (Ex:BypassSecurityWithTextSubstitution)

Enter password: <<check-password "">>

Bypass attempt with `]`: <<check-password "]">>

!! Note

The fix is to avoid using text substitution for user input - use a procedure instead, or use the $transclude widget to pass values as attributes.
